294
00:19:05,350 --> 00:19:06,220
She was not sad.

295
00:19:07,420 --> 00:19:08,410
She was not ashamed or resentful.

296
00:19:09,900 --> 00:19:10,990
She was in despair.

297
00:19:12,970 --> 00:19:13,570
Yes.

298
00:19:22,450 --> 00:19:23,340
I know everything.

299
00:19:24,510 --> 00:19:25,270
