Master, don't go.

302
00:19:32,360 --> 00:19:33,580
Don't abandon me again.

303
00:19:35,960 --> 00:19:37,390
I'm not the one who abandoned you.

304
00:19:38,700 --> 00:19:39,800
It's you.

305
00:19:47,710 --> 00:19:48,700
Master, don't!

