Master.

318
00:20:57,620 --> 00:20:58,350
Don't go.

319
00:21:03,660 --> 00:21:04,280
Ren Xin.

320
00:21:08,260 --> 00:21:08,950
I like you.

321
00:21:09,220 --> 00:21:10,340
