366
00:23:19,640 --> 00:23:20,370
Li Tongguang.

367
00:23:20,400 --> 00:23:21,200
No.

368
00:23:22,220 --> 00:23:23,580
Do you know why I said

369
00:23:23,850 --> 00:23:25,570
