397
00:24:26,080 --> 00:24:26,980
Don't follow me.

398
00:24:29,560 --> 00:24:30,690
Do you understand?

399
00:24:31,940 --> 00:24:32,530
Master.

400
00:24:32,780 --> 00:24:40,770
♫I don't want to wake up; I can't stop missing you♫

